{"generated": "2026-07-19 15:06", "curation": {"market": "개인 투자자 여러분,\n\n지난 24시간 동안의 시장 뉴스를 종합하여 핵심 테마를 브리핑해 드립니다.\n\n<b>1. 한국 경제의 위상 변화와 1인당 GDP 4만 달러 진입 가시화</b>\n최근 한국 경제는 1인당 GDP 4만 달러 진입을 눈앞에 두고 있으며, 이는 5년 만에 최대 폭 증가를 기록할 것으로 예상됩니다. 특히 블룸버그 등 외신은 한국 증시가 글로벌 증시의 투자 심리를 좌우하는 선행 지표로 부상했다고 평가하며, 코스피와 나스닥의 상관계수가 2년래 최고치를 기록했습니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiYkFVX3lxTE9xM3BERmktUjNZWXJ1NHNwa3U4R21sUUtxek5sS1ktLVJVWFV1dm1vdzZvbk5xUFBSVDFfS2NFeEwyTDl1d1pRYXF6RnhuUW5FdUE3VXRPdFBRY0dPdDZNNlp3?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#1</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiaEFVX3lxTE1Oa1BBR0tsYi1yVjBGSmN5RTRCcE1xQUxLdWRCMW93MXNNU2JtVWxLcnZBQTQ2RjFmSWxZTnc3YTA5TEwzSU8yOHV5V3EzTkZOc2VoMmpnZ0dpLWVLd0pFWDhqbUpfYmxF?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#3</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiT0FVX3lxTE0wR0hMdUladVA0aGJ2c2NSZ3h0QTRhUmhOOHVxUk90NlFONzNMMUJwX0Y4UGlSNnNwaVgwQ3J5em1xRVBGMDZjVFpGbkRNc1k?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#4</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiW0FVX3lxTE5VQ1NpLXY5bFJHcTZndlBwdEFfUlJpY3VablViSWVaXzdxN2dkT2p4Mm1aNU1Gem5mOUtEVnN3NTNyOURjZ3VPY0FLR25HU1Z4SlQ2dEZkOHU4YXM?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#7</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiiAFBVV95cUxNOGVRcURiMmo4UkVwTldiMTI3S1BpeUN3V196UzE3WTQ0UkFhbXctZHU5YzNSYktENEpSbjd4M2w1TFJFQ2pOWXFoZkpXcFdxek1Eb1NEbnljbHdxVDJtdmdxWUJIeWlNbzFTQTJkTFhJMHkyelBaTFpGVXI2dnRDWUY0SkR0b2RO?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#8</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMid0FVX3lxTE5oUGZmOHl1clk3cHBIbHpvQkUzaGQ5OWx1QlNoWnduZEh2c3BDd0ZiUHpmNFRJYWhjNHpjelUxYzVib0xBcXZuVEVjQ3BmQ3VXeXd0RFg3TUVtbmRQNGhhamRfLUcxZ1dvTUxNX0xBal9zSTEtLU1n?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#9</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZ0FVX3lxTFA3QmV1NXI3M1NFY0ZnX05iU0R3U2oyR3dJbkt4WnJYUlg4aEdJVWwyQS1ucjN6VE9Oa05WbEtqZlJpX1MxQ3l4TGZPU3pZdGhaZzVtSjBoVlpzQTJEUi1VNnhUbTlJMzg?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" r